<h2>Testing Results</h2>
<h4>View our testing results and certifications</h4>
<a href="/information/downloads/"><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-36527" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/logo-NFRC-1.png" alt="" width="120" height="120" /></a>Solar is dedicated to providing safe, quality products to customers and our in-house test labs offer the unique opportunity to execute tests quickly and efficiently with certification by nationally-recognized third parties.[/vc_cta][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="/applications/commercial/"><img class="alignnone wp-image-38039 size-full" title="Solar Innovations" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/commercial-main-3434.png" alt="Solar Innovations" width="671" height="374" /></a>
<span style="font-size: x-large;">COMMERCIAL</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Solar Innovations<sup>Â®</sup>Â specializes in providing high quality <a href="/applications/commercial/">commercial</a>Â products for a variety of types of businesses.Â From single Terrace Doors to expansive Glass Structures, Solar has you covered in so many ways. Our operable walls can create a dynamic storefront, lobby, or restaurant space that draws visitors in, and skylights or curtain walls provide inviting natural light that can improve customer satisfaction. Your lobby or work space area isn't complete without one of our systems. Whether a restaurant, office space, retail store, hotel, sport venue, or educational or institutional facility, our high quality systems can improve any commercial space.</p>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="/applications/residential/"><img class="alignnone wp-image-38040 size-full" title="Solar Innovations" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/residential-main-3434.png" alt="Solar Innovations" width="671" height="374" /></a>
<span style="font-size: x-large;">RESIDENTIAL</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="/applications/residential/">Residential</a>Â applications can range from simplistic modern style to traditional English structures with a full set of decorative accessories. Solar Innovations<sup>Â®</sup> is your single source provider for all your residential Door &amp; Window, Glass Structure, and Skylight needs, with the ability to fully customize any project. We offer Complete Glazing Packages that keep sightlines, finishes, and glazing warranties consistent. While other manufacturers say no, Solar says yes. We believe there isn't a dream too big or small for your next home project. We can work directly with homeowners, architects, professional builders, contractors, or dealers and we can give you the products you need for your project to succeed.</p>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_column_text]
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Aluminum</h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img class="wp-image-37978 size-full aligncenter" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/material-aluminum-76.png" alt="" width="159" height="191" /></h2>
<p style="text-align: left;">Aluminum products are some of the strongest in the industry. Every product line from Solar is available in durable aluminum. Aluminum is alsoÂ recognized for its sustainable nature, ability to support larger sizes and in addition, durability and longevity compared to other materials. Â We provide Doors &amp; Windows, Glass Structures, and Skylights in aluminum.</p>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_column_text]
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Vinyl-Composite</h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone wp-image-37980 size-full" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/material-vinyl-98.png" alt="" width="159" height="191" /></h2>
<p style="text-align: left;">Vinyl-composite is another versatile option for Doors &amp; Windows. Vinyl-composite is a naturally thermally efficient material, allowing our products to reach higher energy codes and reduce heating and cooling costs. Similar to aluminum, vinyl-composite framing is durable and requires no constant finish maintenance.</p>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_column_text]
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Solid Wood</h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone wp-image-37981 size-full" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/material-wood-99.png" alt="" width="159" height="191" /></h2>
<p style="text-align: left;">The warmth and beauty of solid wood can complement any home or commercial space. Solid wood is available in a variety of species and finishes on select Door &amp; Window, Structure, and Skylight products. For products that will come into direct contact with the elements, durable aluminum cladding is available for the exterior.</p>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_column_text]
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Wood Cladding &amp; Veneering</h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone wp-image-37979 size-full" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/material-veneer-78.png" alt="" width="159" height="191" /></h2>
<p style="text-align: left;">For those interested in combining the strength of aluminum or vinyl-composite and the natural beauty of a wood interior, wood cladding and veneering are a great choice. Wood cladding is a thick wood cap on the interior, while wood veneering is a thin layer of wood; both options provide the beauty of real wood and the longevity of an aluminum or vinyl-composite product.</p>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_column_text]
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-36897 size-full" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/made-in-usa-icon.png" alt="" width="159" height="102" /></h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Made in America</h2>
All our products are designed and manufactured in the United States at our state-of-the-art facility in Pine Grove, PA.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_column_text]
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-37450" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/coastal-icon.png" alt="" width="91" height="102" /><span style="font-size: 16px;">Â </span></h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Coastal Applications</h2>
Our systems have the option to be both coastal and non-coastal. Because we use stainless steel hardware, our materials withstand the corrosive effects of the elements in these coastal regions.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_column_text]
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-36821 size-full" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/hurricane-impact-icon-small-1.png" alt="" width="102" height="102" /></h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Hurricane Impact Rated</h2>
Our company currently offers the largest selection of products tested for Florida ratings. As a result, the products withstand even the most extreme weather conditions.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_column_text]
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-36827 size-full" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/monster-sizes-icon-small.png" alt="" width="62" height="102" /></h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Monstrous Sizes</h2>
Solar Innovations<sup>Â®</sup> has the ability to manufacture even larger panels that operate with greater ease for several functions: folding, sliding, swinging, and stacking.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_column_text]
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-36820 size-full" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/thermal-break-icon-small-1.png" alt="" width="150" height="102" /></h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Thermally Enhanced</h2>
The thermal break separates the aluminum and minimizes conductivity of heat and cold from the inside to the outside while ensuring the structure's interior remains comfortable at any time of year.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_column_text]
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-36899 size-full" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/engineering-icon.png" alt="Custom Engineering for Custom Glazed Windows and Doors" width="120" height="102" /></h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Custom Engineered</h2>
Each Solar Innovations<sup>Â®</sup> systemÂ is custom made to order based on your project needs and preferences. Therefore, our team of engineering experts has you covered.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_column_text]
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-36822 size-full" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/Ease-of-Operation-icon-small-1.png" alt="" width="69" height="102" /></h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Ease of Operation</h2>
Solar Innovations<sup>Â®</sup>' systems offer single-handed operation resulting in smooth movement with little effort. Because much of our hardware is manufactured in-house, we have greater control of lead times.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_column_text]
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-36902 size-full" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/hardware-icon.png" alt="" width="86" height="102" /></h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Vertical Integration</h2>
In addition to manufacturing ourÂ products, we also make many components for ourÂ hardware. This allows us to better control lead times and as aÂ result, help serve our customers better.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_column_text]
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-36901 size-full" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/glass-options-icon.png" alt="" width="65" height="102" /></h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Glass Variety</h2>
Solar Innovations<sup>Â®</sup> has top of the line glazing solutions which include laminated, dual glazed, triple glazed, and marine glazed options just to name a few.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_column_text]
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-36903 size-full" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/recylcled-material-icon.png" alt="" width="102" height="102" /></h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Sustainable Products</h2>
Solarâ€™s products are manufactured with outstanding thermal performance, durable framework, andÂ sustainable materials, therefore making it a great option for your next project.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_column_text]
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-36904 size-full" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/screen-option-icon.png" alt="" width="73" height="102" /></h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Screen Options</h2>
Screen options are available on a wide variety of our door and window products. These screen options help keep the pests at bay still allowing you to view the outdoors.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_column_text]
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-36920 size-full" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/multiple-styles-icon.png" alt="" width="107" height="102" /></h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Multiple Styles</h2>
Solar Innovations<sup>Â®</sup> manufactures the highest quality glazed structures custom designed and engineered to match individual customers' needs while having a large variety of styles to choose from.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_column_text]
<h2>Single Source Provider</h2>
At Solar Innovations<sup>Â®</sup> Architectural Glazing Systems, we are always innovating new products and technologies while serving dealers, architects, and homeowners in the architectural building materials community. We provide high-end products that are sustainable and also increase the efficiency of either a residential home, commercial building, and high-end resort. Crafted with precision and quality, ourÂ products enhance the richness of any lifestyle, and also bring the outdoors in while keeping the harsh elements out.

As your single source provider of Residential and Commercial products we provide: Stacking Glass Walls, Folding Glass Walls, Multi-Stacking Doors, Multi-Pocket Doors, Lift Slide Doors, Sliding Glass Doors, Pivot Doors, Terrace Doors, Sunrooms, Greenhouses, Conservatories, Skylights, Wood and Aluminum Curtain Walls, Tilt Turns, Doors, Windows, Glass Railings in addition to many other products. Furthermore, we are confident we can the suit the needs of any situation for your next project.

We offer complete solutions to fit your needs in our Doors &amp; Windows, Glass Structures, and Skylights. Our products create open environments that give an awe factor to any home or commercial building, while increasing natural light and reducing utility costs. Contact us today for a free quote.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]
